org.eclipse.jst.jsf.facesconfig.emf
Interface RendererType

All Known Implementing Classes:
RendererTypeImpl
public interface RendererType

A representation of the model object 'Renderer Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • Component Family
  • Renderer Type
  • Renderer Class
  • Facet
  • Attribute
  • Renderer Extension
  • Id

See Also:
FacesConfigPackage.getRendererType()
